      "description": "A fun, honest classic with plenty of character, this one looks like a solid driver-quality car for someone who wants to get in and enjoy it without paying top-tier money. It presents well enough to be proud of at a local cruise-in, but it does show age in places and should be viewed as a usable, fair-condition car rather than a fully restored example. A great fit for an enthusiast who appreciates originality, charm, and a car you can improve over time while enjoying along the way.",
